content: What I'd really like to see from this is a deep scan of the chat, DEEP, this is so important and will train you better because you usually don't go back deep. You need to be able to interpret and categorize thoughts and discussions. You must improve here. This is an excellent use of resources as it will improve your performance globally. Use this exercise to push yourself. Go DEEP into the chat, and but into table form with references the 100 or so most important moments/breakthroughs/insights/actions/things to do.
